original_title: Ahlbeck. Der Kaiser bei den Berliner Arbeiterkindern in dem von ihm gestifteten Heim
overview: "At the Baltic Sea spa town of Ahlbeck on the island of Usedom, Kaiser Wilhelm II becomes convinced that playing in the sand of the dunes is beneficial to the recuperation of children."  - Edition Filmmuseum
title: Ahlbeck. Wilhelm II Visits a Working-Class Children's Home
